data.value:
A cold glass of milk is a thing of joy, and nobody should have to miss out. Get the delicious Horizon Organic® milk you love, without lactose.
Grade A Reduced Fat Organic Milk, Lactase Enzyme**, Vitamin A Palmitate, Vitamin D3.
Ingredient Grade A Reduced Fat Organic Milk, Lactase Enzyme**, Vitamin A Palmitate, Vitamin D3.
Type of Milk:
Organic Lactose-Free Reduced Fat Milk (Cow's milk)
Ingredients:
Grade A Reduced Fat Organic Milk
Lactase Enzyme
Vitamin A Palmitate
Vitamin D3
Allergens:
Contains milk
This product contains milk proteins (casein and whey), so it is not suitable for individuals with a milk allergy, but it is safe for those with lactose intolerance.
Storage Instructions:
Refrigeration required: Keep refrigerated at a temperature of 0°C - 4°C (32°F - 40°F).
Opened: Best consumed within 7-10 days after opening.
Unopened: Store in a cool, dry place before opening, and check expiration date.
Product Intended For:
Lactose-intolerant individuals: This milk is designed for those who can’t digest lactose but do not have a milk allergy.
People looking for a reduced-fat, organic milk alternative.
Where to buy: Walmart U.S. , Whole Food MArket New York
